<![CDATA[<font face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><p class="MsoNormal"></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><table align="center" width="600" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><tbody><tr><td align="left" colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="542" bgcolor="#ffffff"><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I wanted to let you know about an opportunity that might be of interest.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#1155cc" face="arial, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="http://www.stepforward.uk.com"><img src="https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/FyGQDUw_HOzaYuzKg5W5vFKlBH5QryesK_0DuccX7Fv9NOpvJMRllN3bkV3kkql-_e803Uwdsf4NSevrQbLcefUKlQ4DvKSeXN4xSmOxf2vlBU9D3XdhcMkIvxv5=s0-d-e1-ft#http://www.stepforward.uk.com/templates/workfirst/images/logo-trans.png" alt="" width="200" height="43"></a></font></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif"><div>In September we will launch our first Step Forward&nbsp;programme. This programme gives school leavers&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">from all backgrounds their first experience of the workplace.</span></div></font></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">We’ve had over 1000 applicants for the programme and have selected 50&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">highly motivated and engaged</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;young people.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Currently we are looking for organisations that might be interested in employing one or more of these apprentices.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thanks to government funding, they are available for a whole year at a cost of just £9,154 to employers, which&nbsp;makes this a great opportunity to get an extra person in your team at a very reasonable price (while&nbsp;also doing some real good).&nbsp;</span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">We’re planning to take eight ourselves as it’s such a good deal!</span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Please click the logo for more information and do get in touch if you are interested. We will get someone from the Step Forward team to give you a ring or alternatively you could contact jeyanti.yorke@the-challenge.org.</span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Kind regards,</span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Barney Harker</span></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="line-height: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>]]></td>
